      "id": "PopularPost352819",
      "post_content": "I wonder why they felt the need to specify that only your attacking *non-walls* count. Did testing show that people were attacking with their walls when this was out, thinking it enabled that? Was it because they knew, someday, that a set would come out in which Walls would finally have their day, and the only thing between us and a ruinous bad future was to put that there?",
      "posted_by": "NobuTheBard",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost352819\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">I wonder why they felt the need to specify that only your attacking <i>non-walls</i> count.  Did testing show that people were attacking with their walls when this was out, thinking it enabled that?  Was it because they knew, someday, that a set would come out in which Walls would finally have their day, and the only thing between us and a ruinous bad future was to put that there?</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '352819'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy101359\">NobuTheBard</span>\r\n                                (11/27/2013 6:08:14 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../..